## Development
```bash
git clone https://github.com/baljotchohan/CIVION
cd CIVION

# Install in dev mode
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Build frontend
./scripts/build_frontend.sh

# Run tests
pytest

# Release
./scripts/release.sh 2.0.1
```

